snippet.title: Tekkouki Mikazuki Trial Edition
snippet.description: This is quite a rare game and was Sandlot's first PlayStation 2 title 9it prototyped a lot of the tech they used in later games too). It's quite clumsy in terms of control but remains decently fun nonetheless.
